query:
query getWardrobeShellsQuery($width: Int!, $depth: Int!, $height: Int!, $wardrobeType: String!, $shutterType: String, $categoryId: Int!, $subCategoryId: Int!, $cityId: Int!, $projectCreationDate: String, $orderProfileType: orderProfileType!) {
  getWardrobeModules(width: $width, depth: $depth, height: $height, wardrobeType: $wardrobeType, shutterType: $shutterType, categoryId: $categoryId, subCategoryId: $subCategoryId, cityId: $cityId, projectCreationDate: $projectCreationDate, orderProfileType: $orderProfileType) {
    nucleusModuleId
    moduleName
    moduleImage
    applicableSections
    moduleDimension {
      dimensionId
      dimensionName
      width
      depth
      height
      __typename
    }
    offsets {
      moduleId
      section
      width
      depth
      height
      offsetX
      offsetY
      offsetZ
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
